data.text:
Our Franklin Lakes, NJ Funeral Home

When looking for a local, family funeral home in Franklin Lakes to assist you in the burial or cremation of a deceased family member, what makes ours worthy of your attention? It's our rich legacy of service, affordable prices and the elegance of our facilities. But more than any of those things, it’s our considerate, supportive and highly professional staff. If we can be of service to you now or any time in the future, don’t hesitate to call the number listed in the top right corner of this page.

Are you here to leave a condolence message, share a memory, or to view a loved ones Book of Memories™ online tribute? If so, you'll find the tributes for those we have had the honor to care for during the past two months highlighted in the box above.

Learn more about cremation by browsing our extensive Cremation Services section. If you have questions about our services, funeral pre-planning, or would like any additional information, we ask you to call us at the number listed in the top right corner of this page. You may also send an email using the form on our contact us page. Vander Plaat-Vermeulen Memorial Home, the leader among family funeral homes in Franklin Lakes NJ, is here for you.
